        <h2>We imagine the world for you, so that you no longer have to.</h2>
        <div class="our-vision-statements">
          <p class="our-vision-statement1">Our goal is simple: to explore what is considered a negative product of our DNA and deliver beautiful outcomes. We describe our work as an accurately inaccurate portrayal of living with a neurological condition. We do not visualise conditions on a factual basis, instead we put it to the people to direct our work and we do so to perfection.</p>
