    <div class="sub-content">
      <div class="our-vision-contents">
        <h2>Pushing the boundaries of human intellect.</h2>
        <div class="our-vision-statements">
          <p class="our-vision-statement1">We exist to challenge our perception by questioning the extent of our present knowledge. On record, there are over 600 neurological conditions, affecting up to 1 billion people and counting. Experiential education in VR is now considered the new effective tool to engage with audiences. We want to reform public understanding through use of this technology to deliver artistic recreations of real life experiences, educating about first aid and spreading awareness of our biological differences.</p>
          <p>We aim to exceed medical knowledge and finally show people the real life stories of those who want their experiences visually expressed.</p>
        </div>
